; Engine-B reference implementation for tick-combat (Godot 4 / GDScript).
; Per addendum §6: tests data_behavior_separation in a non-ECS, actor/
; object-tree, GC'd engine — paradigmatic distance from xtreme/Bevy ECS.
;
; Substituted for Unreal Blueprints (the D-008 pick) because Unreal is not
; installable in the current execution environment. The substitution
; trades away the Blueprint-graph-absorbs-design test; it keeps the
; cross-engine trajectory test + the actor/object-model data_behavior_
; separation test.

config_version=5

[application]
config/name="tick-combat (Godot reference)"
config/features=PackedStringArray("4.6")
